\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c89aa56bb93524e8410f338161f29766e5f8f2","tid":2385475,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"他曾整理過背囊，不可能沒發現裡面的萬用刀，故不接納被告的辯解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n汁過背囊D野又一定會由零開始汁架咩...<br />\n通常細細舊又唔重, 都照放响背囊..."},{"pid":"da67a5cf69585da9afbf44504a7317cd35e68264","tid":2385475,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623ea5e9bd17ac02a54487da0278f79d9d9ec4d6","tid":2385475,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"官指涉案萬用刀可用來拆毀欄杆、移除地磚等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裁判官指被告搜出的泳鏡、望遠鏡、勞工手套等都是堵路人士常用物品。涉案萬用刀可以用來拆毀欄杆，移除地磚等，因此根據被告招認和環境證據，裁定被告罪成。被告需還押至 2 月 19 日求情和判刑。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80%E7%AD%89-%E4%B8%80%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E7%84%A1%E7%BD%AA-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E8%AD%A6%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B-%E7%B5%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%B2%97%E7%96%8F%E5%A4%A7%E6%84%8F%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2588%2580%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B2%2597%25E7%2596%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%25B1%25A1%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1wwRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=505bd0e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2588%2580%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B2%2597%25E7%2596%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%25B1%25A1%2F&h=00830a0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80%E7%AD%89-%E4%B8%80%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E7%84%A1%E7%BD%AA-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E8%AD%A6%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B-%E7%B5%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%B2%97%E7%96%8F%E5%A4%A7%E6%84%8F%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1/</a>"}]}